Package com.trikset.control

Provides interfaces and classes for device I/O access and control.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IGamepad  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnalogSensor Class for reading analog inputs. 
    Battery Class for power management of peripheral devices. 
    DigitalSensor Class for reading digital inputs. 
    Encoder Class for reading value from encoder. 
    Gamepad Class for manage a gamepad. 
    I2cCommunicator Class for I2C (Inter-Integrated Circuit Bus) device access. 
    Led Class for manage a light-emitting diodes (LED). 
    PowerMotor Class for controlling power motors. 
    Sensor3d Class for controlling a device for measuring or maintaining orientation. 
    ServoMotor Class for controlling servomotors.
